00:33:15.660 --> 00:33:18.840
and just maybe there's a
class of planets out there

00:33:18.840 --> 00:33:26.610
where this transition to cognitive
function as a part and technology

00:33:26.610 --> 00:33:29.920
as a part of the way the
planet functions has become

00:33:29.920 --> 00:33:31.330
something long-term.

00:33:31.330 --> 00:33:34.600
And there's some fascinating
arguments that I don't have time

00:33:34.600 --> 00:33:38.880
