possible, whether intelligent--

00:33:38.880 --> 00:33:41.980
"intelligence" is something
that always will limit itself

00:33:41.980 --> 00:33:45.870
by giving itself the power to
wipe itself out or could we be

00:33:45.870 --> 00:33:48.210
