had a space program

00:33:48.210 --> 00:33:49.880
and therefore survived
the extinction

00:33:49.880 --> 00:33:51.810
by pushing the asteroid
out of the way.

00:33:51.810 --> 00:33:53.950
There are ways in which you
could imagine technology leads

00:33:53.950 --> 00:33:55.360
