00:34:45.690 --> 00:34:48.930
I would submit that this
new boundary we're going

00:34:48.930 --> 00:34:53.080
through could be an eon boundary
and I propose the name Sapiezoic,

00:34:53.080 --> 00:34:55.940
for what we're entering,
the phase of Earth

00:34:55.940 --> 00:34:59.310
that is characterized by wisdom.

00:34:59.310 --> 00:35:01.100
Now, that seems sort of arrogant.

00:35:01.100 --> 00:35:04.460
In fact, it was arrogant of the
